data.description:
Elegant single-family home within a central neighborhood.

This stylish and elegant single-family home offers absolute comfort and the convenience that comes with living in a highly desirable community. Everything you could ever need is only moments away including shopping centers, dining options, schools and a host of brand new amenities.
The light-filled layout spans 1,925sqft and boasts three good-size bedrooms and two full baths plus a flex room that could be adapted to suit your needs.

Daily life will center around the open-concept kitchen, dining and living room with direct access to the paved outdoor area for hosting guests. For those who love to cook, a large island and stone countertops await in the kitchen along with a pantry, a tiled backsplash and a suite of stainless steel appliances.
You can leave the car in the attached two-car garage and walk to the neighborhood park plus you'll also live within the prized Socorro School District which has ranked third in the nation over the past year.
